; SAT: 16-bit counter reaches 0xFFFF (needs 65535 BMC steps)
; Tests BMC scalability with deep unrolling
; Expected: SAT (at step 65535) — use --bound 200 for reasonable test
1 sort bitvec 16
2 sort bitvec 1
3 zero 1
4 state 1 count
5 one 1
6 add 1 4 5
7 next 1 4 6
8 init 1 4 3
9 constd 1 200
10 eq 2 4 9
11 bad 10
